(62, 'Suhas Subramanyam Makes History as the First Indian American Elected from Virginia and the Entire East Coast! ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡³ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸', 'image1-1730966945887-20603484.png', '[\"news\",\"latest\"]', 'suhas-subramanyam-makes-history-as-the-first-indian-american-elected-from-virginia-and-the-entire-east-coast-', '<p>A groundbreaking achievement for the Indian American community! Suhas Subramanyam has made history by becoming the first Indian American elected to represent Virginiaâ€™s 87th district, as well as the first to win a seat from the entire East Coast. This historic victory is a testament to the growing influence of the Indian American community in U.S. politics.</p><p>As one of the youngest members in the U.S. legislature, Suhas is focusing on crucial issues like healthcare reform and economic growth, advocating for policies that resonate with the future of our nation.</p><p>This victory paves the way for more representation and brings a fresh perspective to the legislative process. ğŸ‰</p><p>ğŸŒ Join The Global Indians Community and be part of a growing network of changemakers! Visit <a href=\"http://www.globalindiansinfo.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.globalindiansinfo.com</a></p><p>ğŸ“± Join our WhatsApp group: <a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT</a></p><p>#IndianAmericans #HistoryInTheMaking #SuhasSubramanyam #DiversityInPolitics #Leadership #GlobalIndians #USPolitics #EastCoastRepresentation</p>', '2024-11-07 13:39:15'),
(63, 'Exciting Career Opportunities for Indians in Sweden!', 'image1-1731475847738-497610436.png', '[\"news\",\"latest\",\"jobs\"]', 'exciting-career-opportunities-for-indians-in-sweden', '<p>Sweden\'s new visa rules, effective from 2025, are set to open more high-paying job opportunities for Indian professionals, especially in fields like&nbsp;<span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">STEM</span>&nbsp;(Science, Technology, Engineering, and Mathematics). The Swedish government\'s latest directive includes reduced salary thresholds and more flexibility for&nbsp;<span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Blue Card</span>&nbsp;holders, allowing them to switch jobs without the need to reapply for a new card.</p><p><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">In-demand roles include:</span>&nbsp;ğŸ”¹ Software &amp; System Developers</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Cyber Security Specialists</p><p>ğŸ”¹ AI &amp; Machine Learning Experts</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Cloud Engineers</p><p>ğŸ”¹ IT Architects</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Game Developers</p><p><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Engineering sector job openings:</span>&nbsp;ğŸ”¹ Mechanical Engineers</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Electrical Engineers</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Industrial Engineers</p><p>ğŸ”¹ Chemical Engineers (especially those in renewable energy and battery production)</p><p>Sweden offers competitive salaries, particularly in tech and engineering, making it an ideal destination for skilled professionals seeking new challenges and opportunities in 2025!</p><p><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Join the Global Indians Community!</span></p><p>Be part of a growing network of changemakers and explore these exciting career opportunities!</p><p>Visit&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.globalindiansinfo.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: var(--link);\">www.globalindiansinfo.com</a>&nbsp;for more details.</p><p>ğŸ“± Join our WhatsApp group:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: var(--link);\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT</a></p><p>#SwedenJobs #IndianProfessionals #STEMCareers #TechOpportunities #EngineeringJobs #GlobalIndians #BlueCard #AIJobs #MachineLearning #CloudComputing #CyberSecurity #RenewableEnergy #ChemicalEngineering #JoinTheMovement #GlobalNetworking #CareerOpportunities #TechIndustry #EngineeringCareers #Sweden2025</p>', '2024-11-13 11:00:52'),
(64, ' Meet Bharat Desai, an Indian-American Entrepreneur Whose Current Net Worth is Rs 13,500 Crore', 'image1-1731561837943-389212579.png', '[\"latest\",\"technology\",\"news\"]', '-meet-bharat-desai-an-indianamerican-entrepreneur-whose-current-net-worth-is-rs-13500-crore', '<p>Bharat Desai, an Indian-American billionaire and former Tata Consultancy Services (TCS) employee, exemplifies the entrepreneurial spirit that turns dreams into reality. Today, with a net worth of approximately Rs 13,501 crore (around $1.6 billion USD), Desaiâ€™s story is both inspiring and instructional for aspiring entrepreneurs.</p><p>From IIT Bombay to Americaâ€™s Tech Scene</p><p>Desaiâ€™s journey began in 1976 when he moved from India to the United States after completing his studies in electrical engineering at IIT Bombay. His first role was as a programmer with TCS, where he met his future wife, Neerja Sethi. Sharing a mutual interest in creating their own enterprise, the couple took a bold step in 1980, founding their IT consulting and outsourcing firm, Syntel, from their small apartment in Troy, Michigan, with an initial investment of just $2,000 (around Rs 1.65 lakh).</p><p>The early days of Syntel were challenging, with the company generating only $30,000 in revenue during its first year. However, Desai and Sethiâ€™s vision and dedication gradually paid off, as Syntel gained a strong foothold in the IT services market, eventually expanding across North America, Europe, and Asia.</p><p>A Legacy of Innovation and Success</p><p>Bharat Desaiâ€™s leadership and foresight helped Syntel grow into a globally recognized IT consulting and outsourcing powerhouse, ultimately leading to its acquisition by French technology giant Atos in 2014 for $3.4 billion.</p><p>Desaiâ€™s entrepreneurial journey underscores the importance of perseverance, vision, and the ability to seize opportunities in the fast-paced world of technology and business. Today, as a highly successful businessman, Desai continues to inspire aspiring entrepreneurs across the globe.</p><p>For more details about Bharat Desai\'s journey and his impact on the tech industry, visit <a href=\"http://www.globalindiansinfo.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.globalindiansinfo.com</a>.</p><p> Join our WhatsApp group for more inspiring success stories: <a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT</a></p><p>#BharatDesai #Entrepreneurship #IndianAmerican #TechIndustry #SuccessStory #Innovation #Syntel #Inspiration #GlobalIndians</p>', '2024-11-14 10:54:03'),
(65, 'Sehgal Foundation Receives the Prestigious 5th National Water Award! ', 'image1-1731665075431-470472612.png', '[\"news\"]', 'sehgal-foundation-receives-the-prestigious-5th-national-water-award-', '<p>We are thrilled to announce that <strong>Sehgal Foundation</strong>, a remarkable Indian-American initiative, has been honored with the <strong>5th National Water Award</strong> for its exceptional contributions to water conservation and sustainable management across rural India. ğŸ’§</p><p>Through their groundbreaking projects in rainwater harvesting, groundwater recharge, and community-driven water management, the foundation has transformed countless communities by ensuring equitable access to clean and safe water. This award recognizes their tireless efforts in tackling water scarcity and empowering rural populations.</p><p>This recognition reflects the foundationâ€™s unwavering commitment to enhancing the lives of millions and contributing to the broader goal of national water sustainability. ğŸŒ</p><p>Let\'s celebrate their remarkable success and inspire more innovative solutions for a water-secure future. ğŸ™Œ</p><p>For more inspiring success stories, visit <a href=\"http://www.globalindiansinfo.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.globalindiansinfo.com</a>.</p><p>ğŸ’¬ <strong>Join our WhatsApp group for more updates</strong>: <a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/IBD5TnnlJA5JPNy3JSylxT</a></p><p>#WaterConservation #Sustainability #SehgalFoundation #NationalWaterAward #Innovation #CommunityEmpowerment #RuralDevelopment #India #GlobalIndians #SuccessStory #WaterManagement</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>4o mini</p>', '2024-11-15 15:34:38');
